cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a new method for ensemble learning and lifelong learning using neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves natural language processing tasks, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
